{"id":4803,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/4803","type":2,"name":"ナイトウィザード The ANIMATION","name_cn":"暗夜魔法使","summary":"以安洁洛特为首的世界守护者们一直在和贝尔瑟法为首的恶魔们为了争夺世界而进行着不断的斗争。然而，当看似平凡的少女志宝艾莉丝出现后，一切都发生了变化……\r\n\r\n\r\n《暗夜魔法使》（ナイトウィザード，英：Night Wizard!），是2002年由Enterbrain出版的桌上角色扮演游戏（TRPG），作者为F.E.A.R.公司的菊池たけし。2007年10月又发行了第二版规则书。\r\n本作以现代社会为舞台，描写暗中守护世界的魔法使们的活跃，是带有轻小说风格的Low Fantasy属作品。其世界设定的氛围，受到Alice Soft的游戏《夜が来る!》的强烈影响。像Gunner's Broom、Witch Blade这样的机械式魔法之帚，成为了该作的标志性物品。\r\n此游戏通过在与TRPG无关的杂志上连载官方Replay，启用声优在Net Radio上发布情报等手段，逐渐聚集了不小的人气。其派生作品有PC上与之同名的成人游戏，以及2008年2月在PS2上发售的AVG游戏。 《Fami通PLAYSTATION+》自2007年6月号开始也连载此作相关漫画《Night Wizard! Variable Witch》。\r\n由HAL FILM MAKER制作，衔接第一版与第二版的动画，于2007年10月到同年12月在日本播出。","eps":[{"id":34691,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34691","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":2,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34692,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34692","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34693,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34693","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34694,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34694","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":4,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34695,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34695","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34696,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34696","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34697,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34697","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34698,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34698","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":34699,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/34699","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"",